Megatron turned to Skullgrin, "That is enough Decepticons, Skullgrin,
get that filthy Maximal off of you." as he raised his fist, and fired
off a blast of raw fusion energy into the air to accent his point.

Soundwave looked on, much had happened since arriving on earth, with his
D.E.D comerades leaving recently. But this was a chance to start a new
era, and someone begged for chaos. "Rumble, Spasstik, eject, oporation,
warfare." He brought his hand up to his shoulder, and pressed his
button, as his cassette door came open, and released a blue cassette,
"Eject" then a grey one, "Eject." They both transformed, and landed on
the ground, as Rumble held out his laser rifle, and aimed it at Alpha
Dolphy. 

"Okay you stupid rust bucket, back away from our buddy there."

Spasstik wasted no time, leaping forward, and begining to rush the robot
nearing Skullgrin, snarling the whole way.
